            <title><![CDATA[Battlefield 6 Dev Says Supporting Xbox Series S "Was A Challenge," But Similar To PC Targets]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/battlefield-6-dev-says-supporting-xbox-series-s-was-a-challenge-but-similar-to-pc-targets/1100-6534745/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
